name: JamNotes
tagline: An iOS app for tracking the setlists played at live concerts.
body:
# JamNotes
## A tool for the obsessed live music aficionado, JamNotes provides a clean, simple interface for tracking setlists from your favorite live shows.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with JamNotes? Drop a line to phil@bubblehouse.org.
